Introduction

Queendom (Korean: 퀸덤; Japanese: クイーンダム), formerly known as Sixth Sense (식스센스), was a three-member girl group under ANJ Entertainment. They released a pre-debut single "Barbie Bunny" on May 26, 2015 before officially debuting on October 4, 2016 with the single "Feel Me".
